        "To complement the Random Forest Regressor, an ARIMA (AutoRegressive Integrated Moving Average) model will be implemented. ARIMA models are specifically designed for time series data, capturing temporal dependencies and patterns such as trends and seasonality through differencing, autoregressive, and moving average components.\n",
